ting team, and will need to communicate with them effectively and create a smooth working relationship 2. Ability to multi-task and prioritize - You will service more than one client at a time - you are expected to be able to multi-task as well as prioritize according to milestones, client needs and urgency of task at hand 3. Accountability - You will be responsible for the success of the marketing campaign 4. Able to handle stress - You will need to manage short deadlines and also put your crisis management skills to work as a part of this role. You are expected to be able to think quickly and calmly, and execute on solutions quickly 5. Independent worker - We are looking for individuals who are able to work independently on their own and effectively in a team 6. Presentation skills - You need to be able to craft presentations and whitepapers, as well as be able to present them 7. Interest or knowledge in blockchain - We hope for you to have some interest or knowledge in blockchain and cryptocurrencies 8. Creative thinking - We are looking for individuals who are able to come up with new ideas and creative ways of marketing. You will also be expected to actively contribute to brainstorming sessions for pitches, proposals and projects 9. Social media savvy - You are expected to be social media savvy and be able to create content on-the-go Skills Marketing, Communication, Team-Player, Organised, Leadership Compensation SGD 2,200 - 2,700 monthly ",
